Equals and Hashcodes method:
Let's Say you want to check the equality of the Object.
You Retirved the Object from the Persistance Layer.
And then Modify the Object.
If you test the Equality of the Object with the equals method, Hibernate will return objects are not equal.
So better to implements equals method and hashcode methods with only specefic fields to check the equility.

Its Recommended to use equals and Hashcode
